{"id":"1af14b11aafb2d65c42e5acc3ca49e2a763f1c84f9270d1cf7b54a5c769a9d33","item_id":"cf6c1ff1a0:0","text":"RenderMan 细分曲面使用"}
{"id":"21c45ac41c49f16a990f65c42ac2e38012c85b0766a6d6e9b45a94a93394b711","item_id":"cf6c1ff1a0:1","text":"Pixar 的 OpenSubdiv"}
{"id":"638d8fe33c6ab7b9cfb5427cefeeabc6d02e6366f4c63c796ed48202c283596a","item_id":"cf6c1ff1a0:2","text":"来确保始终渲染出最平滑、最干净的几何体。这样可以避免因多边形镶嵌细分不佳而产生的渲染伪影，例如暗边和轮廓线。"}
{"id":"9457444c368df491fb2a5082f3748c9fce3cca026065722763efaa8c24992d46","item_id":"cf6c1ff1a0:3","text":"使用 RenderMan 细分曲面是首选工作方式，不过 RfB 也支持 Blender 的 Subdivision Surface modifier（细分曲面修改器）。但请注意，对 RenderMan 而言，这是一种效率较低的细分曲面渲染方式，因为 Blender 会比 RenderMan 计算更多面。"}
{"id":"0d0260bf281c2ddc4fbc549fd2ce5b7253373f3b511d9f09c479e0515c10fa14","item_id":"cf6c1ff1a0:4","text":"使用以 RenderMan 为中心的工作流也能保持 viewport（视口）轻量，因为 SubD（细分曲面）成本只会在渲染时产生，从而释放原本会花在视口上的宝贵 GPU VRAM。"}
{"id":"07a8ec1c9566d237d6cfd01372f6a08e4a4e32a76296552cbdb1fd636f38d800","item_id":"cf6c1ff1a0:6","text":"细分曲面（Subdivision Surfaces）"}
{"id":"0895e3ea3d207f413c6e9c0870ef6824c14f2142a3f719d7dabf315b55a20792","item_id":"cf6c1ff1a0:7","text":"了解更多信息。"}
{"id":"581ec3b9f551e32551d3211d978227292243a395e1b9dea7e03b1b8801dad82c","item_id":"cf6c1ff1a0:8","text":"也可以使用未定义 normals（法线）的多边形再进行细分；RenderMan 会为你计算 normals。"}
{"id":"baa02ed14ee9a61db86b5526535fa98096617991e5fade8edf1f23186f555582","item_id":"cf6c1ff1a0:9","text":"RenderMan 细分"}
{"id":"aba393257663786a4f9180a225958f3684dc3016b1f4d28590d4059793df8a5d","item_id":"cf6c1ff1a0:10","text":"渲染细分曲面的首选方式是使用"}
{"id":"50ddfc95f8692db972d9dabb1c80c87b03c2d1420b6176079eebcda1d68d495a","item_id":"cf6c1ff1a0:11","text":"Convert to RenderMan Subdiv（转换为 RenderMan Subdiv）"}
{"id":"7e3ff328aba282bfc95f3714f41241d9c51ea8b43e64c66cbc4b85f390cff091","item_id":"cf6c1ff1a0:12","text":"操作器。"}
{"id":"2d07636984ca7db5fb0401fa4ad39b4ac5084f602eedfb925f7a2dd6e4bd8b37","item_id":"cf6c1ff1a0:13","text":"可以在视口的 RenderMan 菜单中找到它。任何选中的 mesh（网格）都会转换为 OpenSubdiv 曲面。"}
{"id":"5e4d320b48b707d79bab7c152e93909e0ad1cfc3779c3b1bdc75a812397d1d93","item_id":"cf6c1ff1a0:14","text":"在这个渲染中可以看到，吉他效果器现在正以细分方式渲染。"}
{"id":"3f1b35d4f46081c5a22f0821b6bf51c56cc85a68694c5f4c236733f2ab406493","item_id":"cf6c1ff1a0:15","text":"也可以进入 mesh（网格）的 data properties（数据属性），修改 Subdivision Mesh 下的 Scheme 设置，以开启或关闭 RenderMan 细分曲面。选择 None 会将该网格作为 polygon（多边形）渲染。"}
{"id":"b3607f9d9a2a4347f15949930fec5c59cf2bb396307d71b527c5bcbef5608432","item_id":"cf6c1ff1a0:16","text":"添加折痕"}
{"id":"bbe2f6cc35204882b0adc395733b9cbc3e5fb9d597c8d9882ca963bdd82a0f92","item_id":"cf6c1ff1a0:17","text":"RfB 也支持 Blender 的 edge creasing（边折痕）。这里我们正在给选中的边添加 crease weights（折痕权重）。"}
{"id": "6863067eb0a2c7499425c6c189b2c88bac55ca754285a6ab1ef37b75b4cfad4d", "item_id": "cf6c1ff1a0:5", "text": "参见"}
